          transliteration: "tvatsamādhivijaye tu yaḥ punar maṅkṣu mokṣarasikaḥ krameṇa vā |\nyogavaśyam anilaṁ ṣaḍāśrayair unnayatyaja suṣumnayā śanaiḥ ||",
