          transliteration: "idaṁ jaganmayavapustava karmabhājāṁ karmāvasānasamayē smaraṇīyamāhuḥ |\ntasyāntarātmavapuṣē vimalātmanē tē vātālayādhipa namō'stu nirundhī rōgān ||",
