          transliteration: "vimalamatirupāttairāsanādyairmadaṅgaṁ\ngaruḍasamadhirūḍhaṁ divyabhūṣāyudhāṅkam |\nrucitulitatamālaṁ śīlayētānuvēlaṁ\nkapilatanuriti tvaṁ dēvahūtyai nyagādīḥ ||",
