          transliteration: "tadīkṣaṇātkāmakalātivihvalō\ndhṛtiṁ vihāya prasasāra tāmayam |\njagāma pāpairatimōhitō bahu\nvyadhatta karmāṇyakhilāni dūṣitaḥ ||",
