          transliteration: "sa vai daśāpatyajāniprasaktadhīḥ\ntayā'dhamastriyā daśamaṁ sutaṁ tadā |\nnārāyaṇāhvayamajījanat prabhō\ntamēva bālaṁ parilālya nirvṛtaḥ ||",
