          transliteration: "nāśnāmi mṛttikāmamba mithyā vadanti bālakāḥ |\nyadi satyaṁ tadā paśya mamāsyaṁ vivṛtaṁ śubhe |\nityuktvā tvaṁ mukhaṁ tasyā vivṛtya pradarśayaḥ ||",
