          transliteration: "evaṁ rāsotsavaṁ kṛtvā gopīmaṇḍalamaṇḍitaḥ |\nbrahmānandarasaṁ dattvā marutpurapate hare |\nsamastāmayaśāntyarthaṁ bhaktānāṁ pāhi sarvadā ||",
