          transliteration: "tvām āgataṁ prekṣya rathasthm ujjvalaṁ\nsā harṣagadgadya vilokayantī |\ntvam apy amuṣyāḥ karāmbhjaṁ haran\nrathaṁ samāropayad antikaṁ priyām ||",
