          transliteration: "tato nṛpāḥ śiśupālapramukhā\nrukmī ca kopād vigalatpratāpāḥ |\nsannaddhsainyā abhipetur uddhatās\ntvāṁ bāladordaṇḍavimarditāṁs tu tān ||",
