          transliteration: "kṣamāṁ śikṣeta pṛthvyāstu vāyor nirlepatāṁ tathā |\npāvakād dāhaśaktiṁ ca nirmalatvaṁ tathaiva ca |\nākāśavat sarvagato na lipyeta kadācana\nevaṁ prakṛtitaścakre gurubodham anuttamam ||",
