          transliteration: "evaṁ nidhāya bhuvane sumahanti kāryā-\nṇyāvṛtya dhāma paramaṁ śritavānasi tvam |\ntasyāvatāracaritāmṛtasevayā ye\ntuṣyanti te khalu labhanti parāṁ ca muktim ||",
